snippet.title: This Magical Girl is a B*tch - Official Act 2 Launch Trailer | Ghouls 4 Games
snippet.description: Act 2 of The Magic Girl is a B*tch is available now on Steam. Check out the trailer for The Magic Girl is a B*tch to meet the characters and get a peek at the story of this visual novel about giving one very grumpy eighth grader too much power.
